        </item>
        <item>
            <title>近半 PS 活躍玩家仍在玩 PS4　Sony：「仍然是事業的重要部分」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/08/50-percent-of-sonys-active-userbase-is-still-on-ps4/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=50-percent-of-sonys-active-userbase-is-still-on-ps4</link>
